HEADWORD: Franklin
<hw>Frank"lin</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>frankelein</ets>; cf. LL. <ets>franchilanus</ets>. See
<er>Frank</er>, <pos>a.</pos>]</ety> <def>An English freeholder, or
substantial householder.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
